node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Drink home ibiza® on July 02, 2021 tagging @robizawine. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text:
Like if you love @robizawine 

This is Carmen & Gerard and we’re glad to show you our Rosé. As you know, we’re new in this and we’re so happy how is going. The feedback of the wine is great and we’re entering in top places. The rosé has fine bubbles, it’s the 1st sauvignon blanc-rosé in Europe #ibiza -inspired with the reflection of the sunset and the magnetism of Es Vedrà. The wine bets for an eco-friendly experience, it’s organic and vegan, with an artisan production. Welcome to the regenerative lifestyle, reconnect with nature & loved ones.

node.text:
🥳 WIN A TASTING MENU EXPERIENCE at @cottonbeachclub paired with @robizawine 🥳 

We celebrate the community growth to 400.000 followers! Enjoy a breathtaking view of the turquoise sea in this special occasion with 3 more friends! How⁉️
 
1️⃣ Like & share this post
2️⃣ Follow @robizawine & @cottonbeachclub 
3️⃣ Tag 1, 2 or 3 friends/couple/family 
 
📍The winner will be announced on June 23th
GOOD LUCK!🍀

node.text:
Born w/ enthusiasm & rewarding efforts... Nace con mucha ilusión y esfuerzo... @robizawine 

A spanish rosé wine, unique of its kind being the 1st sauvignon blanc-rosé of Europe. Fine bubbles with an artisan production & inspired by the boho-chic ibiza style, Robiza has a sophisticated sunset design 🌅 Vegan & organic, is just found in hand-picked restaurants & gourmet stores, promoting a conscious wine-making ♻️ Get your @robizawine today online✔️

#ibiza #ibiza2021 #rosé #wine #rosélover #wineblog

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Drink home ibiza® in Ibiza, Spain with @ashbenis. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Cannot wait to show you our rosé wine, very special... I hope you appreciate it as much as we do!
